      <title>特朗普为何承诺补充美国石油储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/why-trump-plans-to-refill-us-oil-reserve-and-what-it-means-for-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统计划补充美国紧急原油储存系统——用他的话说就是“充到最高”——这将有助于防范未来的油价冲击。但这说起来容易做起来难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/why-trump-plans-to-refill-us-oil-reserve-and-what-it-means-for-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普想“夺回”巴拿马运河。但事情没那么简单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/why-does-trump-wants-the-panama-canal-back-and-can-he-take-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统呼吁美国重新控制巴拿马运河，除非海军和商船的通行费用大幅削减。特朗普拒绝排除使用武力，这让人回想起 19 世纪的炮舰外交时代。虽然尚不清楚特朗普是否只是摆个姿态，但他的要求震动了拉丁美洲，该地区受领土争端的影响比中东和亚洲等地区要小。这表明特朗普愿意藐视条约和愤怒]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/why-does-trump-wants-the-panama-canal-back-and-can-he-take-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于周五访问受灾阿什维尔和洛杉矶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-visit-disaster-hit-asheville-and-los-angeles-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统重返白宫后的首次出访将带他前往北卡罗来纳州的阿什维尔和加利福尼亚州的洛杉矶地区，他曾在这些地方大声批评联邦政府对最近自然灾害的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-visit-disaster-hit-asheville-and-los-angeles-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:18:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大向特朗普表示：我们也对边境问题有抱怨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/canada-to-trump-we-have-complaints-about-the-border-too</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理表示，加强边境安全“符合加拿大人和美国人的利益”，并对从美国向北流动的非法枪支和毒品数量不断增加表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/canada-to-trump-we-have-complaints-about-the-border-too</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 21:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普下令加快美国各地项目审批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-plan-to-speed-permitting-of-projects-across-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令加快联邦许可的发放，以此吸引美国投资并缩短关键能源基础设施的建设时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-plan-to-speed-permitting-of-projects-across-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 20:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称国务院不会“降级”至次要角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/rubio-says-state-won-t-be-relegated-to-secondary-role-anymore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马尔科·卢比奥在担任美国最高外交官后的首次讲话中承诺，确保他现在领导的机构在制定美国外交政策方面不会落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/rubio-says-state-won-t-be-relegated-to-secondary-role-anymore</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 19:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党主导的州就出生公民权计划起诉特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/democrat-led-states-sue-trump-over-birthright-citizenship-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党州检察长于周二对新政府发起了首次法庭斗争，起诉阻止唐纳德·特朗普总统终止在美国出生但父母非法入境或持非永久签证的孩子自动获得美国公民身份的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/democrat-led-states-sue-trump-over-birthright-citizenship-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 17:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
