      <title>特朗普让比索暴跌，Sheinbaum 呼吁“保持冷静”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mexico-must-keep-cool-head-on-trump-orders-sheinbaum-says-m66jyfvz</link>
